page1.title: About Me
page1.content: Hello, I'm Atiq and I enjoy reading, researching & creating things. My interest in coding started, when I heard python in one of a physics videos. . Fast-forward to today, and I’ve the privilege to study in one of the well known college in India UPES located at Dehradun. . Right now, I'm pursuing my bachelor degree in computer science. .
